data09.columns

data09["co-ordinates"] = data09.apply(lambda x: (x["Latitude"],x["Longitude"]), axis=1)

locations = data09["co-ordinates"].tolist()
start = locations[0]

import folium
from folium.plugins import HeatMap

m = folium.Map(width=950,height=700, location=start, zoom_start=12)
HeatMap(locations).add_to(m)
